T1  - General purpose technologies ‘Engines of growth’?
AU  - Bresnahan, Timothy F.
AU  - Trajtenberg, M.
JO  - Journal of Econometrics
VL  - 65
IS  - 1
SP  - 83
EP  - 108
PY  - 1995
